				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/C%E1%BA%A5p-giang-ti%C3%AAn-tr%C3%A0/poem-q8346Hj_4cF4MP4KzsKlew">Cấp giang tiên trà - 汲江煎茶</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/H%E1%BB%93ng-M%C3%B4n-h%E1%BB%99i/poem-PbxW0gs8qUBkSlKj5gZSsg">Hồng Môn hội - 鴻門會</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/author-tbuJ74IPkvZZ32WHu1yvJw">Dương Duy Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/H%E1%BB%AFu-M%E1%BB%B9-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-b%E1%BA%A1o-v%C5%A9/poem-jBDXo_2NdCEhHeGl5Vfxrw">Hữu Mỹ đường bạo vũ - 有美堂暴雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Loan-Gia-l%E1%BA%A1i/poem-njy1Q1udQLv-Q8EVjBhygQ">Loan Gia lại - 欒家瀨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/L%C6%B0-s%C6%A1n-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91-dao/poem-mKsUGPsBX0LZpYI3mupGqg">Lư sơn bộc bố dao - 盧山濮布謠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy-Trinh/author-tbuJ74IPkvZZ32WHu1yvJw">Dương Duy Trinh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Hwang-Jin-i/Ph%C3%A1c-Uy%C3%AAn/poem-aKuBcxAj85ypLiV_4ndxEg">Phác Uyên - 朴淵</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Hwang-Jin-i/author-R6UhyHNkNFGdxXyw4CHMxQ">Hwang Jin-i</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Qu%C3%A1-H%C3%B4-%C4%90%C3%A0-h%C3%A0/poem-_n-MMYpmxVXyCkpV2m9Eww">Quá Hô Đà hà - 過滹沱河</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ho%C3%A0i-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-il2-xU_Q-nIFla-ypApHCA">Trịnh Hoài Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="http